M$6 PAD VSS VSS VSS NMOSE L=2U W=50U AS=225P AD=425P PS=59U PD=67U
* device instance $7 r0 *1 24.5,0 NMOSE
M$7 VSS VSS PAD VSS NMOSE L=2U W=50U AS=425P AD=225P PS=67U PD=59U
